ke":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T11:41:26.000Z","msg":"太嚴"},{"pid":"341cb8b75dcddf0cb3e4336dfed9ac99194ae263","tid":123791,"uid":34206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T12:22:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>可以俾錢d co sec公司開</blockquote><br />\n可否講多D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實都唔guarantee開到<br />\n銀行依家驚到西咁, 少少野都ban左你個application<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個人經驗開d係美國無業務既銀行/中資銀行成功機會大d"},{"pid":"6312f00759081d1deca05e187670cdf8a886ed1f","tid":123791,"uid":3123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T01:19:45.000Z","msg":"其實唔係開唔到，係攔9佢姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cba5d16b8573ea5570fd1ab718441335a13b0eb","tid":123791,"uid":6411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T01:36:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港人好易<br />\n唔係香港人應該較難，怕你洗錢</blockquote><br />\nhsbc d職員問長問短刁難到你唔撚想開</blockquote><br />\n上年開公司， hsbc 開戶口， 三日批左"},{"pid":"8a1a8d2db1fb418025f5d4bfa53b37edc1c2e1ab","tid":123791,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T01:40:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港人好易<br />\n唔係香港人應該較難，怕你洗錢</blockquote><br />\n其實你知唔知咩叫洗錢, 洗黑錢?"},{"pid":"58258cc96fe83933b9ea771ebe19fc95f2b19880","tid":123791,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T01:42:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港人好易<br />\n唔係香港人應該較難，怕你洗錢</blockquote><br />\n其實你知唔知咩叫洗錢, 洗黑錢?</blockquote><br />\n大陸人係講: 花錢, 洗錢.<br />\n香港人係講: 洗錢(使錢), 洗(使)黑錢"}]}